    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road-wear expected of a well-loved car. Under the hood, the engine responds eagerly, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule and recent preventative maintenance. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and comfortable sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of significant blemishes, while all digital displays, climate controls, and safety features function flawlessly. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension provides a smooth, rattle-free ride. This is a complete, reliable package for a buyer who values a car that has been cared for with an eye for detail.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
