      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s still got so much life left in it! It\u2019s been really well-loved and taken care of over the years, so it runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s the perfect reliable companion for someone who wants a solid car without that brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself how smoothly it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
