      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, an engine renowned for its high-revving character and six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels through a functional variable M differential lock. Crucially, the 'Big Three' have been addressed: the rod bearings were replaced, the VANOS system was overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains compliant yet firm, utilizing its original MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry to maintain the chassis balance that defined this era. While the aesthetic reflects its age with minor road wear, the mechanical vitals are robust, with the valvetrain and high-pressure oiling system operating strictly within factory tolerances. This is an excellent opportunity to own a mechanically sorted legend that is ready for the canyon or the track.",
